data.description: Charming home in Harper, Texas! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home features a generously sized kitchen, boasting abundant cabinets and ample counter space. Thoughtfully designed living spaces offer both comfort and functionality, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Step outside into your own private oasis within the expansive backyard, offering endless opportunities BBQ's and gatherings. Carport, storage and RV parking. Don't let this opportunity slip away-make this adorable Harper home yours today!
